# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:35
translate spanish hwb_s10c_cf95ed3e:

    # "There’s an incline, but it’s not too bad. Next to me, Marina spreads her arms out for balance, but I’m confident enough to not need to."
    "Hay una pendiente, pero no es demasiado mala. A mi lado, Marina extiende los brazos para equilibrarse, pero yo tengo suficiente confianza como para no necesitarlo."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:37
translate spanish hwb_s10c_c656df89:

    # "Crossing over to the ruins themselves will be the riskiest part. There’s no cover, and anyone who happens to look over will see us."
    "Cruzar hasta las ruinas mismas será la parte más arriesgada. No hay cobertura, y cualquiera que mire hacia acá nos verá."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:39
translate spanish hwb_s10c_0bf3fea6:

    # "We just have to hope that the tour group has moved to somewhere without a line of sight on us."
    "Solo tenemos que esperar que el grupo turístico se haya movido a algún lugar sin línea de visión hacia nosotros."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:41
translate spanish hwb_s10c_354de79d:

    # Amber "Okay, hurry."
    Amber "Ладно, поторопимся."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s10c_549ff8da:

    # "I grab Marina’s hand again and start to run."
    "Tomo la mano de Marina de nuevo y empiezo a correr."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s10c_046e21dd:

    # "She struggles to keep up, so I slow down a little bit. It takes maybe two minutes from one end to the other."
    "Ella lucha por seguirme el ritmo, así que reduzco un poco la velocidad. Tarda unos dos minutos de un extremo al otro."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s10c_15b959a5:

    # "When we reach the far wall, Marina’s breathing is strained."
    "Cuando llegamos a la pared lejana, la respiración de Marina está agitada."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s10c_71783054:

    # Amber "Don’t do much running, do you?"
    Amber "Ты не из тех, кто любит бегать, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s10c_39824097:

    # Marina "Not… {w=0.4} At… {w=0.4} All…"
    Marina "Совсем… {w=0.4} Не из… {w=0.4} Тех…"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s10c_35e7673a:

    # "Every word is punctuated with a pant."
    "Cada palabra está marcada por un jadeo."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s10c_dea29ce4:

    # "I’m winded too, but fight my lungs to not show it. I have to look strong for Marina"
    "Yo también estoy sin aliento, pero lucho contra mis pulmones para no demostrarlo. Tengo que parecer fuerte para Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s10c_b6e277dc:

    # Amber "Ready for the fun part?"
    Amber "Готова к веселой части?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s10c_65888586:

    # Marina "Is it actually fun?"
    Marina "А она правда будет веселой?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s10c_7cf2b4ba:

    # Amber "Not yet. We’ve still gotta get up there."
    Amber "Пока нет. Нам сначала нужно туда забраться."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s10c_b081197d:

    # "I point to the lip of the cave, a good fifty feet or so above us still."
    "Señalo el borde de la cueva, todavía a unos quince metros o más sobre nosotros."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:79
translate spanish hwb_s10c_65d443cd:

    # "Marina’s face goes pale as she stares at the sheer rock wall in front of us."
    "El rostro de Marina se pone pálido mientras mira la pared de roca escarpada frente a nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s10c_96664427:

    # Marina "We’re not gonna have to climb that, are we?"
    Marina "Мы же не собираемся взбираться по ней, правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s10c_7afd5112:

    # Amber "How else?"
    Amber "А как еще нам туда добраться?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s10c_0c31fab0:

    # "I wait a second for the shock to hit her face before I laugh and shake my head."
    "Espero un segundo a que el impacto llegue a su cara antes de reírme y negar con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s10c_e722ab32:

    # Amber "Just kidding. Come over here."
    Amber "Да я шучу. Идем сюда."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:93
translate spanish hwb_s10c_88558669:

    # "A short distance away is a slope, somewhat steep but not too long. It leads up into part of the cave close to the ruins."
    "A poca distancia hay una pendiente, algo empinada pero no muy larga. Lleva hacia arriba, a una parte de la cueva cerca de las ruinas."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s10c_48c2cc52:

    # Amber "We actually do have to go up this one."
    Amber "Нам нужно забраться по этому склону."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s10c_c879b819:

    # "Her face still looks doubtful."
    "Su rostro aún parece dudoso."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:108
translate spanish hwb_s10c_eba803ad:

    # Marina "I dunno if I can get up that."
    Marina "Не знаю, смогу ли я подняться по нему."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s10c_5f4bc9a6:

    # Amber "Sure you can. It’s easy; look."
    Amber "Конечно сможешь. Это легко; смотри."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s10c_b1e83963:

    # "I hike up a couple steps. Dirt and a bit of gravel tumble down past my feet, but it’s mostly stable."
    "Subo un par de pasos. Tierra y un poco de grava caen bajo mis pies, pero está mayormente estable."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s10c_69a4ede4:

    # Amber "It’s almost all dirt. If it was loose rock we’d be in trouble."
    Amber "Он почти полностью состоит из грунта. Если бы это была скала из рыхлых пород, вот тогда бы у нас были проблемы."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s10c_5b970f75:

    # "Still looking uncertain, Marina takes a careful step up behind me. Then another."
    "Aún con aspecto inseguro, Marina da un paso cuidadoso detrás de mí. Luego otro."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:130
translate spanish hwb_s10c_5295407f:

    # "She slides back down a little bit with each step."
    "Se desliza un poco hacia atrás con cada paso."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:132
translate spanish hwb_s10c_db57fe99:

    # Amber "Try to spread your weight out a little more evenly. You don’t wanna lose your balance and fall over."
    Amber "Постарайся распределить вес более равномерно. Ты же не хочешь потерять равновесие и упасть."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s10c_d6d5c6fd:

    # "By doing what I say, she’s able to reach where I’m standing."
    "Al hacer lo que digo, logra llegar hasta donde estoy parada."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s10c_af46c21c:

    # Amber "Good job. Now just do that like fifty more times."
    Amber "Молодчина. Теперь просто повтори это еще пятьдесят раз."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s10c_25092fbc:

    # "Marina groans, but I’ve already started."
    "Marina gime, pero yo ya he empezado."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s10c_98601ab5:

    # "I glance back behind me. She’s trailing only a couple steps back. For all her worrying, she’s doing okay."
    "Miro hacia atrás por encima de mi hombro. Ella viene solo un par de pasos detrás. A pesar de toda su preocupación, lo está haciendo bien."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s10c_2da8a49d:

    # "I’m just about to compliment her when I feel the earth shift beneath me and my foot slides loose."
    "Estoy a punto de felicitarla cuando siento que la tierra se mueve bajo mis pies y mi pie se resbala."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s10c_75ac5dc0:

    # "With a yelp, I lose my balance, arms flailing as I try not to fall."
    "Con un grito, pierdo el equilibrio, agitando los brazos mientras intento no caerme."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s10c_421919a4:

    # "Then, faster than I can process, Marina’s arm shoots out and grabs my sleeve. She tugs me back upright."
    "Entonces, más rápido de lo que puedo procesar, el brazo de Marina se dispara y agarra mi manga. Me tira hacia atrás para enderezarme."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:168
translate spanish hwb_s10c_552396ab:

    # Marina "Are you okay? Oh my God, is your ankle alright? It’s not broken is it?"
    Marina "Ты в порядке? Боже мой, с твоей лодыжкой все хорошо? Она же не сломана, правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:170
translate spanish hwb_s10c_298c8851:

    # "Panic is clearly painted across her face."
    "El pánico está claramente pintado en su rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s10c_a4ce421c:

    # Amber "No, I’m fine, I’m fine."
    Amber "Нет, я в порядке, я в порядке."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s10c_e0898d36:

    # "The only thing injured is my pride."
    "Lo único herido es mi orgullo."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:180
translate spanish hwb_s10c_8c643f6e:

    # Marina "Are you sure?"
    Marina "Ты уверена?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s10c_58c7f847:

    # Amber "Yeah, thanks. Good save."
    Amber "Ага, спасибо. Отлично подстраховала."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:188
translate spanish hwb_s10c_4d43b7e5:

    # "We climb up the rest of the way together, but slowly."
    "Subimos el resto del camino juntas, pero lentamente."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s10c_7085dd3c:

    # "At the top, both of us stretch and catch our breath."
    "En la cima, ambas nos estiramos y recuperamos el aliento."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s10c_df86999e:

    # Amber "That wasn’t so bad, was it?"
    Amber "Все было не так уж плохо, правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s10c_89f553a7:

    # Marina "Besides the part where you almost died, maybe?"
    Marina "Разве что за исключением той части, где ты чуть не погибла."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s10c_aef11be7:

    # Amber "Pfft, I didn’t almost die. Besides, that’s what I have my sidekick for."
    Amber "Пфф, да не погибла бы я. К тому же на что мне тогда ассистент."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ccab2188:

    # "She gives me a playful shove."
    "Ella me da un empujón juguetón."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s10c_b1c58f7c:

    # Marina "Hey! I told you I’m not the sidekick here."
    Marina "Эй! Я тебе говорила, что я тут не “ассистент”."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s10c_18887aeb:

    # Amber "Uh huh. You’ll still have to earn the title of \"captain.\" Or \"commander?\" Whatever it is."
    Amber "Ага. Но звание “капитана” нужно заработать. Или “командующего”?. Без разницы."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s10c_9b693092:

    # Amber "And you can do that by finding this thing before I do."
    Amber "И ты можешь сделать это, найдя часть сокровища раньше меня."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:234
translate spanish hwb_s10c_61aae061:

    # "Now that we’re actually up in the ruins themselves, it’s more clear just how tough this is going to be. The cave stretches a long way, like a deep scar in the mountain."
    "Ahora que estamos realmente en las ruinas, queda más claro lo difícil que va a ser esto. La cueva se extiende por un largo trecho, como una cicatriz profunda en la montaña."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:236
translate spanish hwb_s10c_6908e9fe:

    # "Delicate clay buildings, some barely as tall as we are, are arranged throughout."
    "Frágiles edificios de barro, algunos apenas tan altos como nosotras, están dispuestos por todas partes."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s10c_8afe96f3:

    # "They say this was a village, but it’s hard to imagine anyone living here. Everything is so cramped and small."
    "Dicen que esto era un pueblo, pero es difícil imaginar que alguien viviera aquí. Todo es tan estrecho y pequeño."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:242
translate spanish hwb_s10c_d9a6e5b4:

    # Marina "Where do you think we should start?"
    Marina "Как думаешь, откуда нам лучше начать?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s10c_3346e94e:

    # Amber "Hard to say. It won’t be anywhere obvious. Remember, people have been studying this place for decades."
    Amber "Трудно сказать. Сокровище не будет спрятано в очевидном месте. Вспомни, люди исследовали это место десятилетиями."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s10c_3a082603:

    # Marina "What if someone already found it? Like, a long time ago."
    Marina "А что если кто-то уже нашел его? Скажем, много лет назад."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:250
translate spanish hwb_s10c_4d601ee1:

    # "I shrug, but that’s probably impossible to see. The sun has now gone entirely down, leaving us in shadowed darkness."
    "Me encojo de hombros, pero probablemente eso es imposible de ver. El sol ya se ha puesto por completo, dejándonos en una oscuridad sombría."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s10c_1ad4ff4c:

    # "I wonder why Marina doesn’t seem bothered by it this time."
    "Me pregunto por qué Marina no parece molestarse esta vez."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:254
translate spanish hwb_s10c_6fd8058a:

    # Amber "If they did, then I haven’t heard anything about it. We’ve just gotta start looking. Try to be careful though."
    Amber "Если и нашли, то я ничего об этом не слышала. Нам просто надо начать искать. И будь осторожна."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s10c_249dbb96:

    # Marina "I feel bad being here… Maybe this was a bad idea."
    Marina "Мне здесь не по себе… Может это была плохая идея."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s10c_1215149a:

    # Amber "Be super careful, then."
    Amber "Просто будь невероятно осторожна."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:262
translate spanish hwb_s10c_cc654aef:

    # Amber "And watch for spiders."
    Amber "И остерегайся пауков."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:266
translate spanish hwb_s10c_b8373254:

    # "I flick on the spare flashlight and pass it to her. Just in time to see the look of disgust at the mention of spiders."
    "Enciendo la linterna de repuesto y se la paso. Justo a tiempo para ver su gesto de disgusto al mencionar las arañas."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s10c_c7d5c86d:

    # "We split up, staying close to each other but not overlapping where we look. I get down on my hands and knees, shining lights into every corner and cranny that I can."
    "Nos separamos, manteniéndonos cerca pero sin superponer las zonas que revisamos. Me pongo en manos y rodillas, iluminando cada rincón y grieta que puedo."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s10c_bf410bbb:

    # "I worry that our lights might be visible from a distance, even though they aren’t very powerful."
    "Me preocupa que nuestras luces puedan verse desde lejos, aunque no sean muy potentes."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s10c_e7948ae1:

    # "The only alternative would be sneaking over in broad daylight, and we’d be much more likely to be caught then."
    "La única alternativa sería colarnos a plena luz del día, y entonces sería mucho más probable que nos atraparan."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s10c_feb633ed:

    # "I’m not finding anything except dirt. I brush my fingers along the clay bricks in hopes of finding a loose stone or secret compartment, but there's nothing like that."
    "No encuentro nada más que tierra. Paso los dedos por los ladrillos de barro con la esperanza de hallar una piedra suelta o un compartimento secreto, pero no hay nada así."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s10c_346697e2:

    # "Nearby, Marina’s doing the same thing. She’s hitched up her dress so that it doesn’t drag on the ground, and I force myself to look away, rather than stare."
    "Cerca, Marina está haciendo lo mismo. Se ha subido el vestido para que no arrastre por el suelo, y me obligo a mirar hacia otro lado, en lugar de quedarme mirando."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s10c_2a01fcc2:

    # "She offers quite a view, though."
    "Aunque ofrece una vista bastante buena."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s10c_d28945a9:

    # "After a moment, Marina giggles. I’m not sure why."
    "Al cabo de un momento, Marina suelta una risita. No sé por qué."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:293
translate spanish hwb_s10c_8eb41fce:

    # "I haven’t spoken at all, because I don’t want our voices to echo in the cave and give us away. But silently searching gets tedious fast, so I decide to try whispering."
    "No he hablado nada, porque no quiero que nuestras voces resuenen en la cueva y nos delaten. Pero buscar en silencio se vuelve tedioso rápido, así que decido intentar susurrar."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:297
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ce8a217c:

    # Amber "What’s so funny?"
    Amber "Что смешного?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:301
translate spanish hwb_s10c_e686c4e2:

    # Marina "I dunno. Everything, I guess. I was just thinking how weird this is."
    Marina "Я не знаю. Все, наверное. Я просто думала, насколько это странно."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:303
translate spanish hwb_s10c_7af8b732:

    # Marina "Like, it’s just so random, you know?"
    Marina "В смысле, это все такая случайность, понимаешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:307
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ea953570:

    # Amber "Alright, Aristotle."
    Amber "Ладно, Аристотель."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:311
translate spanish hwb_s10c_031c4591:

    # Marina "Who’s that?"
    Marina "Кто это?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:317
translate spanish hwb_s10c_4168040c:

    # Amber "Never mind."
    Amber "Не важно."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:321
translate spanish hwb_s10c_cc12b81c:

    # Amber "But yeah. It is kinda crazy."
    Amber "Но согласна. Это какое-то сумасшествие."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:323
translate spanish hwb_s10c_73c266d5:

    # "Deciding that the building I was scouring is a lost cause, I move on to the next one."
    "Decidiendo que el edificio que estaba registrando es una causa perdida, paso al siguiente."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s10c_1bd9c126:

    # Marina "I know it’s probably not a big deal for you since you do this stuff all the time, but this is honestly the most fun I’ve ever had. I think."
    Marina "Я знаю, что для тебя это не ахти какое дело, потому что ты занимаешься подобными вещами все время, но для меня, честно, это самое веселое, что мне приходилось делать, я думаю."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s10c_612a76e6:

    # Amber "Destroying ancient Native American landmarks?"
    Amber "Разрушать древние достопримечательности американских индейцев?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:333
translate spanish hwb_s10c_254969d3:

    # Marina "I’m being careful! Super careful! But just in general. Being out here on the road."
    Marina "Я осторожна! Очень осторожна! Но я говорю в общем. Быть за пределами города."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s10c_15233628:

    # Marina "I thought maybe I was making a mistake when I left but not anymore."
    Marina "Сначала я сомневалась, что, может быть, совершила ошибку, уйдя из дома, но теперь я так не думаю."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:341
translate spanish hwb_s10c_a665b1c0:

    # Amber "I’m glad."
    Amber "Я рада."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:343
translate spanish hwb_s10c_0319066c:

    # "And I am. I really am."
    "Y lo estoy. De verdad."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:345
translate spanish hwb_s10c_c41e39f8:

    # Amber "Guess it worked out well for both of us."
    Amber "Думаю, для нас обеих все сложилось наилучшим образом."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:347
translate spanish hwb_s10c_f83b1d57:

    # "I can’t see her from here, but I know she’s smiling."
    "No puedo verla desde aquí, pero sé que está sonriendo."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:349
translate spanish hwb_s10c_368cedf1:

    # "Then she giggles again."
    "Luego vuelve a reírse."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:353
translate spanish hwb_s10c_fc1c4500:

    # Marina "Aw, Amber, you’re a big ol’ softie after all, aren’t you?"
    Marina "Оу, Эмбер, ты, оказывается, еще та добрячка, не так ли?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:357
translate spanish hwb_s10c_cb3df833:

    # Amber "Am not!"
    Amber "Не так!"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:361
translate spanish hwb_s10c_a9e84de4:

    # Amber "I take it back, I should’ve left you on the side of the road."
    Amber "Беру слова обратно; лучше бы я оставила тебя на обочине."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:369
translate spanish hwb_s10c_87033dda:

    # "This time we both laugh. After that, we lapse back into near-silence. Just the sound of us crawling around, or occasionally moving to another building to search."
    "Esta vez nos reímos las dos. Después de eso, volvemos al silencio casi total. Solo el sonido de nosotras gateando, o de vez en cuando mudándonos a otro edificio para buscar."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:377
translate spanish hwb_s10c_48b76afa:

    # "Soon, the happy atmosphere starts to dissolve as we start getting frustrated."
    "Pronto, el ambiente alegre empieza a disiparse mientras comenzamos a frustrarnos."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:379
translate spanish hwb_s10c_9f59e04f:

    # "Or at least I do."
    "O al menos yo lo hago."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:381
translate spanish hwb_s10c_39fbee53:

    # "It takes maybe 20 minutes before we’ve looked over all the buildings. There aren’t too many, and combing over them isn’t that hard."
    "Tarda unos 20 minutos en que hayamos revisado todos los edificios. No hay muchos, y peinarlos no es tan difícil."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:383
translate spanish hwb_s10c_a4c36010:

    # "But we don't find anything."
    "Pero no encontramos nada."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:385
translate spanish hwb_s10c_4e29d729:

    # "Not even a clue or hint that we’re in the right spot."
    "Ni siquiera una pista o indicio de que estamos en el lugar correcto."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:391
translate spanish hwb_s10c_3ab0cb62:

    # "Sighing through my nose, I start double-checking some of the larger homes."
    "Suspirando por la nariz, empiezo a revisar dos veces algunas de las casas más grandes."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:393
translate spanish hwb_s10c_092a4aec:

    # "All the crawling and bending is starting to take a toll on me. When I straighten up, my back is sore, and sweat presses my hair to my forehead."
    "Tanto gatear y agacharse está empezando a pasarme factura. Cuando me enderezo, me duele la espalda y el sudor me pega el cabello a la frente."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:395
translate spanish hwb_s10c_44b42917:

    # "We should’ve brought some bottles of water with us."
    "Deberíamos haber traído algunas botellas de agua con nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ba2b58a2:

    # "I lean against a rock wall and massage my shoulders. Marina finishes up a building, then joins me."
    "Me apoyo contra una pared de roca y me masajeo los hombros. Marina termina con un edificio y se une a mí."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:404
translate spanish hwb_s10c_957ccccb:

    # "She’s biting her lip, frowning a little."
    "Se muerde el labio, frunciendo un poco el ceño."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:406
translate spanish hwb_s10c_fae17202:

    # Marina "Any luck?"
    Marina "Что-нибудь нашла?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s10c_969810cb:

    # Amber "Nope, nothing. You?"
    Amber "Неа, ничего. А ты?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:414
translate spanish hwb_s10c_741019d8:

    # Marina "Uh uh."
    Marina "Неа."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s10c_bd63282c:

    # "We both pause, silent."
    "Ambas hacemos una pausa, en silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:418
translate spanish hwb_s10c_400eb135:

    # Marina "Soooo..."
    Marina "Тооо есть..."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:420
translate spanish hwb_s10c_e3aa5200:

    # Marina "That’s it, right? Like, we’ve checked all the buildings."
    Marina "Это все, да? В смысле мы осмотрели все постройки."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s10c_552d8d05:

    # Amber "Can't be."
    Amber "Этого не может быть."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s10c_6aab4778:

    # Amber "We must have missed something. I’m going to try checking out the cave itself."
    Amber "Мы, должно быть, что-то упустили. Я попробую осмотреть саму пещеру."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:428
translate spanish hwb_s10c_5017dc9a:

    # "She just stands there."
    "Ella solo se queda ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:433
translate spanish hwb_s10c_4a83de8b:

    # "Watches as I head over to the far side."
    "Observa mientras me dirijo al otro lado."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:435
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ebe0e7fc:

    # "I shine my flashlight up and down and up again, examining every inch of the rock."
    "Enciendo y apago mi linterna una y otra vez, examinando cada centímetro de la roca."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:437
translate spanish hwb_s10c_993cda9e:

    # "There's gotta be a crevice where the gold is stashed."
    "Tiene que haber una grieta donde esté escondido el oro."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:439
translate spanish hwb_s10c_a223c6a4:

    # "Or some other hiding place."
    "O algún otro escondite."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:441
translate spanish hwb_s10c_d472f024:

    # "There has to be."
    "Tiene que haberlo."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:443
translate spanish hwb_s10c_49212047:

    # "But none of the cracks are wide enough or deep enough for something like that."
    "Pero ninguna de las fisuras es lo suficientemente ancha o profunda para algo así."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s10c_7a09c985:

    # "A few minutes later and I pass by Marina, still in the same place."
    "Unos minutos después, paso junto a Marina, que sigue en el mismo lugar."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s10c_63a6b146:

    # "I check her face as I go. Her eyebrows are furrowed, and she looks worried."
    "Miro su rostro al pasar. Tiene las cejas fruncidas y parece preocupada."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:452
translate spanish hwb_s10c_d5224095:

    # "I keep hunting."
    "Sigo buscando."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:456
translate spanish hwb_s10c_b15cb1ff:

    # "Images of Mariah triumphantly holding up the gold spur me on."
    "Las imágenes de Mariah sosteniendo el oro triunfalmente me impulsan a seguir."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s10c_d460f77c:

    # "Just the thought of her smug grin pisses me off."
    "Solo pensar en su sonrisa arrogante me enfurece."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:463
translate spanish hwb_s10c_c1724aa2:

    # "When I reach the other other end of the cave, I double back and check it again."
    "Cuando llego al otro extremo de la cueva, retrocedo y reviso de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:468
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ded17c8a:

    # "And again."
    "Y otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:473
translate spanish hwb_s10c_8fdd7b30:

    # "Finally, Marina pulls away from the wall. I hear it, but don't see it."
    "Finalmente, Marina se separa de la pared. Lo escucho, pero no lo veo."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:478
translate spanish hwb_s10c_beda1336:

    # Marina "Amber, come on."
    Marina "Эмбер, ну же."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:480
translate spanish hwb_s10c_655e7b14:

    # Marina "There's no way."
    Marina "Здесь ничего нет."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:484
translate spanish hwb_s10c_d894ebaf:

    # "Her voice is a knife in my heart."
    "Su voz es un cuchillo en mi corazón."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:486
translate spanish hwb_s10c_d90deb15:

    # "It hurts because I know she's right."
    "Duele porque sé que tiene razón."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:488
translate spanish hwb_s10c_32a12353:

    # "I sigh and flick off my flashlight."
    "Suspiro y apago mi linterna."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:490
translate spanish hwb_s10c_90387c0f:

    # "Standing there, I look at the invisible ground and have to admit the truth to myself - it’s not here."
    "De pie, miro el suelo invisible y tengo que admitir la verdad para mí misma: no está aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:492
translate spanish hwb_s10c_f23db1b4:

    # "There’s no treasure to be found in the Mummy Cave Ruins."
    "No hay tesoro que encontrar en las Ruinas de la Cueva Momia."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:496
translate spanish hwb_s10c_279706fa:

    # "Either we got it wrong, or someone beat us to it. Whichever the answer, there’s nowhere else in here that it could be."
    "O nos equivocamos, o alguien nos ganó. Sea cual sea la respuesta, no hay ningún otro lugar aquí donde pueda estar."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:501
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ee24d774:

    # "I make my way back to Marina, slowly."
    "Regreso hacia Marina, lentamente."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:507
translate spanish hwb_s10c_bbc064ca:

    # "I can feel stinging tears of frustration beginning to well up in my eyes, which surprises me."
    "Siento lágrimas punzantes de frustración comenzar a acumularse en mis ojos, lo que me sorprende."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:509
translate spanish hwb_s10c_c5535b6a:

    # "I'm sure Mariah would be laughing at me if she was here right now."
    "Estoy segura de que Mariah se estaría riendo de mí si estuviera aquí ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:511
translate spanish hwb_s10c_26f31c01:

    # "Abruptly, I stop walking towards her and spin around. I don’t want Marina to see."
    "De repente, dejo de caminar hacia ella y doy media vuelta. No quiero que Marina lo vea."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:513
translate spanish hwb_s10c_18ae1dc9:

    # "There’s the sound of crunching dirt as she walks over."
    "Se escucha el crujido de la tierra mientras se acerca."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:517
translate spanish hwb_s10c_252ed066:

    # Marina "Amber?"
    Marina "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:519
translate spanish hwb_s10c_f98344f1:

    # "There’s worry in her voice."
    "Hay preocupación en su voz."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:523
translate spanish hwb_s10c_24868161:

    # "I shake my head. I don’t know if she can see."
    "Sacudo la cabeza. No sé si ella puede verme."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:528
translate spanish hwb_s10c_4b669a70:

    # "She lays her hand on my shoulder, and two tears manage to leak out of my eyes. I shake my head again."
    "Apoya su mano en mi hombro, y dos lágrimas logran escapar de mis ojos. Vuelvo a sacudir la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:530
translate spanish hwb_s10c_55f1876e:

    # Marina "Amber? Amber, it’s okay."
    Marina "Эмбер? Эмбер, все хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:532
translate spanish hwb_s10c_3673cd6c:

    # Amber "No, I’m sorry. I screwed up. I was wrong."
    Amber "Нет, мне жаль. Я облажалась. Я была неправа."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:534
translate spanish hwb_s10c_67f9a296:

    # Amber "There’s nothing here."
    Amber "Здесь ничего нет."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:538
translate spanish hwb_s10c_2183c36e:

    # Marina "I know there isn’t. Seriously, that’s okay."
    Marina "Я знаю, что нет. Серьезно, все в порядке."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:540
translate spanish hwb_s10c_1b95b34c:

    # "I sob, not even knowing why."
    "Sollozo, sin siquiera saber por qué."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:542
translate spanish hwb_s10c_fd040f71:

    # "Dammit. Dammit."
    "Maldición. Maldición."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:544
translate spanish hwb_s10c_c42ca53e:

    # "Get a grip, Amber. I wrench my eyes shut, before the waterworks really start. It burns, but I manage to hold back."
    "Cálmate, Amber. Aprieto los ojos con fuerza, antes de que el llanto realmente comience. Quema, pero logro contenerme."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:546
translate spanish hwb_s10c_4189f0ed:

    # "Taking deep breaths, I get myself under control."
    "Tomando respiraciones profundas, recupero el control."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:558
translate spanish hwb_s10c_6d3e5066:

    # "I sink down to lean against the wall of the cave. Marina does the same."
    "Me dejo caer para apoyarme contra la pared de la cueva. Marina hace lo mismo."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:560
translate spanish hwb_s10c_800aa701:

    # "Our clothes are dusty from being on the ground so much."
    "Nuestra ropa está polvorienta de tanto estar en el suelo."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:562
translate spanish hwb_s10c_fdfab65b:

    # "Marina pokes me in the side."
    "Marina me da un codazo en el costado."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:564
translate spanish hwb_s10c_bb3c955b:

    # Marina "You okay?"
    Marina "Ты в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:566
translate spanish hwb_s10c_96adabb4:

    # "I draw a rattly breath."
    "Respiro con dificultad."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:568
translate spanish hwb_s10c_2a8720a5:

    # Amber "Yeah, I’m fine. Sorry, I don’t know what that was about. I just got… Super frustrated."
    Amber "Да, я в норме. Прости, я не знаю, что на меня нашло. Я просто…невероятно расстроилась."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:570
translate spanish hwb_s10c_12386173:

    # Marina "Yeah, I could tell."
    Marina "Да уж, я заметила."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:572
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ab0541ac:

    # Amber "Can it."
    Amber "Отвали."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:574
translate spanish hwb_s10c_86c4bbca:

    # "I flick her, gently, on the knee."
    "Le doy un golpecito suave en la rodilla."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:576
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ca3be727:

    # Amber "But uh, that was kind of embarrassing."
    Amber "Но э-э, это было немного неловко."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:580
translate spanish hwb_s10c_c28831f2:

    # Marina "No, it’s okay! Really. I cry all the time at home, don’t worry."
    Marina "Нет, все в порядке! Правда. Я все время плачу дома, не переживай."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:582
translate spanish hwb_s10c_2dd800fa:

    # Amber "It’s just… It’s like losing. Not finding the treasure, I mean. So I’m mad for wasting all our time on this."
    Amber "Просто это… Это как поражение. Не найти сокровище, я имею в виду. Поэтому я злюсь, что потратила столько нашего времени на это."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:584
translate spanish hwb_s10c_4d994652:

    # Amber "Aren't you?"
    Amber "А ты нет?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:588
translate spanish hwb_s10c_fe79913e:

    # Marina "No, why would I be?"
    Marina "Нет, с чего бы мне злиться?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:592
translate spanish hwb_s10c_8bc9f8a2:

    # "She sounds genuinely surprised."
    "Suena genuinamente sorprendida."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:594
translate spanish hwb_s10c_221d048d:

    # Amber "Because now we’re behind on the next one, too. What if someone beats us to all the rest of them?"
    Amber "Потому что теперь мы на шаг позади в поисках следующего кусочка паззла. Что если кто-то опередил нас и нашел все остальные части?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:596
translate spanish hwb_s10c_66301235:

    # Marina "Now you sound like me."
    Marina "А сейчас ты говоришь как я."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:598
translate spanish hwb_s10c_c79617a9:

    # Amber "Oh God, is there a cure?"
    Amber "О Боже, это излечимо?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:600
translate spanish hwb_s10c_9c0fb36d:

    # Marina "Meanie."
    Marina "Вредина."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:602
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ca5c6fa5:

    # Marina "But really."
    Marina "Ну правда."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:604
translate spanish hwb_s10c_141be0c3:

    # Marina "I had fun, so I don’t think it was a waste of time."
    Marina "Я повеселилась, поэтому не считаю все это тратой времени."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:606
translate spanish hwb_s10c_f18438b9:

    # Marina "Even if we’re not like, super rich now. I’m glad we came here."
    Marina "Даже если мы и не получили несметные богатства. Я рада, что мы приехали сюда."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:608
translate spanish hwb_s10c_0817652e:

    # "Once again, I don’t even have to look to know she’s smiling. She’s always smiling, after all."
    "Una vez más, ni siquiera necesito mirar para saber que está sonriendo. Después de todo, siempre sonríe."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:610
translate spanish hwb_s10c_bef1446f:

    # "It’s one of the cuter things about her, and there are lots of those."
    "Es una de las cosas más lindas de ella, y hay muchas de esas."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:612
translate spanish hwb_s10c_c14267a8:

    # "But I’m afraid to look up and meet her eyes. Afraid because of what I’ve been starting to feel lately, and how I’ve been thinking of her."
    "Pero tengo miedo de levantar la vista y encontrarme con sus ojos. Miedo por lo que he empezado a sentir últimamente, y por cómo he estado pensando en ella."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:614
translate spanish hwb_s10c_50c7b262:

    # "It’s stupid to get bothered by this now, I know. We’ve been together all day."
    "Es estúpido molestarme por esto ahora, lo sé. Hemos estado juntas todo el día."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:616
translate spanish hwb_s10c_17adf32f:

    # "But right now, when I’m already being over-emotional, I feel like it’d be a bad idea."
    "Pero ahora mismo, cuando ya estoy siendo demasiado emocional, siento que sería una mala idea."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:618
translate spanish hwb_s10c_252ed066_1:

    # Marina "Amber?"
    Marina "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:620
translate spanish hwb_s10c_3bb08a3b:

    # "And then, by reflex, I do it anyway."
    "Y entonces, por reflejo, lo hago de todas formas."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:622
translate spanish hwb_s10c_3e88d016:

    # "I look over, and I was right. My heart flutters a little. But the smile I was anticipating has been replaced by yet another look of concern."
    "Miro hacia ella, y tenía razón. Mi corazón revolotea un poco. Pero la sonrisa que anticipaba ha sido reemplazada por otra mirada de preocupación."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:624
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ed28a5ef:

    # Amber "Yeah, you’re right. I guess it wasn’t so bad."
    Amber "Да, ты права. Думаю, все было не так плохо."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:626
translate spanish hwb_s10c_ccdcc6cf:

    # "She brightens up immediately."
    "Se ilumina de inmediato."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:628
translate spanish hwb_s10c_65ca8eea:

    # Marina "For real?"
    Marina "Правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:630
translate spanish hwb_s10c_19e08fb2:

    # Amber "Mhm. I’m good now. Still, sorry for freaking out there for a sec."
    Amber "Мм. Сейчас я в порядке. И все же извини, что я взбесилась на секунду."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:632
translate spanish hwb_s10c_9951e413:

    # Marina "It’s okay. Don’t feel bad."
    Marina "Все хорошо. Не переживай."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:651
translate spanish hwb_s10c_33e9d855:

    # "Groaning, I stand up again. I’m definitely gonna be sore tomorrow."
    "Gimiendo, me levanto de nuevo. Definitivamente voy a estar adolorida mañana."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:655
translate spanish hwb_s10c_36a045e7:

    # Amber "We should get out of here though. Longer we spend, the more likely we are to get caught."
    Amber "Но нам нужно отсюда убираться. Чем дольше мы здесь остаемся, тем больше вероятность, что нас поймают."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:657
translate spanish hwb_s10c_048862bd:

    # "It’s been probably 45 minutes or so since we ditched the tour group. Hopefully they didn’t get search and rescue out looking for us."
    "Han pasado probablemente unos 45 minutos desde que abandonamos el grupo del tour. Ojalá no hayan enviado a búsqueda y rescate a buscarnos."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:666
translate spanish hwb_s10c_19f60543:

    # "I offer my hand to Marina, who’s still sitting on the ground. She takes it, and I haul her to her feet."
    "Le ofrezco mi mano a Marina, que todavía está sentada en el suelo. La toma, y la levanto hasta ponerla de pie."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:679
translate spanish hwb_s10c_7ad3c8f4:

    # "After dusting herself off, we both walk to the edge of the cave. It’s impossible to see anything. Even the trail across the way is invisible from here."
    "Después de sacudirse el polvo, ambas caminamos hasta el borde de la cueva. Es imposible ver nada. Incluso el sendero al otro lado es invisible desde aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:681
translate spanish hwb_s10c_d2a8169e:

    # Amber "Watch your step going down the hill."
    Amber "Смотри под ноги, когда будешь спускаться по склону."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:683
translate spanish hwb_s10c_2e0e1180:

    # Marina "Yeah, we don’t want anyone to almost die again."
    Marina "Ага, мы же не хотим, чтобы кто-то снова почти не погиб."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s10c_95151aa2:

    # "I’m winded too, but fight my lungs to not show it. I have to look strong for Marina."
    "Yo también estoy sin aliento, pero lucho contra mis pulmones para no demostrarlo. Tengo que parecer fuerte para Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s10c.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s10c_425fade1:

    # Amber "Uh- huh. You’ll still have to earn the title of \"captain.\" Or \"commander?\" Whatever it is."
    Amber "Ага. Но звание “капитана” нужно заработать. Или “командующего”?. Без разницы."

